---
Title: The Lyric In A Time of War
By: Eloise Klein Healy
Source:
  URL: https://www.poetryfoundation.org/poems/52850/the-lyric-in-a-time-of-war
  Locus:
    Date: 15 June 2018
  Source:
    Title: The Islands Project
    Publisher: Red Hen Press
    Copyright: 2007
Format: verse
---
Let my music be found wanting
in comparison
to yours (as it must)

let me be found loving
(as you were)
extravagantly the beautiful

let me find you
and the song (forever)
between us

in these terrible times
